<seg id="2995">This card card only appears if for at least one built-in file system space limitation (quota) is activated and initialized (recognizable by the file quota.user / quota.group on the file system). here you can change parameters for each user, whereby the space constraints are given in KB:</seg>
<seg id="2996">These parameters can be individually set for each filesystem. the current file system is selected by means of the field file system with space restriction.</seg>
<seg id="2997">The card card groups informs about the group's members belonging to the selected user. the standard group, which belongs to the user, can be found in the Primary group. furthermore, the user can become a member in other groups by selecting them in the large field.</seg>
<seg id="2998">The dialog properties of the group contains a list of all users. to add a user to the group, select this user in the list.</seg>
<seg id="2999">To add a user or group, select Add from the user or group menu or click the appropriate Add button on the toolbar. editing or deleting the selected user or group will work analogue.</seg>
<seg id="3000">With this module you can install the LILO bootstrap, add, remove and change the boot password, change the time to boot of the standard operating system, remove the standard operating system, remove, change operating systems, remove, change, and more.</seg>
